ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Tuktut Nogait National Park of Canada) Order
PrecisOrder 1) repealing the Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Tuktut Nogait National Park), made by Order-in-Council P.C. 2011-743 dated June 23, 2011; and 2) making the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (TUKTUT NOGAIT NATIONAL PARK OF CANADA) ORDER to support the proposed expansion of the Tuktut Nogait National Park in the Northwest Territories for the period beginning on the day on which this Order is made.
